@Jawshewah- the rating system is not overall quality of the film, but quality based on the category it's in.  This is a TS, so it's not going to be the same quality as a DVDrip or BRrip, and anybody who expects it to be is an idiot.  That's why each source is/should only be graded against similar examples of the same source.  That way a TS is only being judged against other TSs, DVDrips are only being judged against other DVRrips, etc.
